These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Flower: lily, aconite
Sport: skiing, water-polo
Transport: roller, taxi
1. Sport:skiing is on the right of Transport:roller##1
2. Flower:aconite is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Flower   | aconite    | lily |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite
Food: lime, watermelon
Transport: motorbike, train
1. Transport:train is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
2. Food:lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Food   | watermelon | lime  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

